quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,"By the fig and the olive [of Jerusalem]"
  95,2,"and by Mount Sinai [of Egypt]"
  95,3,"and by this secure city [of Makkah]"
  95,4,Surely We have created man in the best form
  95,5,then We will reduce him to the lowest of the low
  95,6,except those who believe and do righteous deeds; they will have a never-ending reward
  95,7,"Then, what makes you deny the Judgment Day"
  95,8,Is not Allah the Most Just of all judges